            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"音乐制作-music-production\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#音乐制作-music-production\">#</a> 音乐制作 / Music production</h1>\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"item\" title=\"Sibelius V2020.6 for MacOs\"><span class=\"exturl image\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL3JidmNuYnltNS5obi1ia3QuY2xvdWRkbi5jb20vQXZpZCUyMFNpYmVsaXVzJTIwVWx0aW1hdGUlMjB2MjAyMC42JTIwbWFjT1Muemlw\" data-background-image=\"https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/echoflove/echoflove.github.io@latest/images/404.png\"></span>\n          <div class=\"info\">\n          <span class=\"exturl title\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL3JidmNuYnltNS5obi1ia3QuY2xvdWRkbi5jb20vQXZpZCUyMFNpYmVsaXVzJTIwVWx0aW1hdGUlMjB2MjAyMC42JTIwbWFjT1Muemlw\">Sibelius V2020.6 for MacOs</span>\n          <p class=\"desc\">打谱软件西贝柳斯</p>\n          </div></div></div>",
